Class JsonModelServer<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the input class, i.e. String
    O - type of the output class, i.e. Sentiment

    public class JsonModelServer<I,O>
extends SameDiffJsonModelServer<I,O>
    This class provides JSON-based model serving ability for Deeplearning4j/SameDiff models Server url will be http://0.0.0.0:{port}>/v1/serving Server only accepts POST requests
    Author:
    raver119@gmail.com, astoyakin
